\id 1JN Matupi Chin Standard Bible
\h 1JOHAN
\toc1 1JOHAN
\toc2 1Johan
\toc3 1Jn
\mt1 JOHAN CAPAT
\mt3 A Pacuek Nah
\mt4 (John’s First Letter)
\is2 JOHAN CAPAT KAWNG
\im Johan he Jesuh Khrih kah hnukbang cuek la om. Pathen aka tangnah Khrihca rhoek long he a tholhnah Pathen taengah a phoe atah Pathen loh khodawk a ngai vetih tholh a khoe pah ni” a ti (1.9).
\ip Khat neh khat lungnah he tangnah taktak la a om (3.11-24). Pathen tah lungnah la a om dongah a pilnam he amah mueiloh la om saeh (4.1-21). Tholhnah n'ta he ni tanah taktak la a om. Jesuh tah Pathen capa, Khrih la om tih duek taktak ti hing koep ti tangnah ham om (5.1-12). Johan capat he AD 85-95 vaengah a tael.
\iot Sawt Yoeinah
\io1 Ol loh hingnah n'paek \ior (1. 1-4)\ior*
\io1 Pathen tah vangnah neh Khrih tah mamih kah awtkoi \ior (1. 5—2. 6)\ior*
\io1 Olpaek thai \ior (2. 7-17)\ior*
\io1 Khrih kah rhal neh Pathen ca rhoek \ior (2. 18—3. 10)\ior*
\io1 Pathen neh Mamih kah lungnah \ior (3. 11—4. 21)\ior*
\c 1
\s1 Olrhannah
\p 
